“Listen” Visual Out Soon 
Shot and edited by @bekaedao 
Fruitless is on the way you guysss 🤍

fruitless out 12/12. 
I’m so proud of this project & all the hard work that’s gone into it. From recording all day to late night mix sessions, I got a chance to explore my sound & get comfortable with my voice. At the time, my time with romance ending & I was surrounded by unhealthy habits. Music became my therapy to deal with these issues and become vulnerable, allowing me to come to acceptance. I am only coming up on a year now as an artist & didn’t imagine expanding upon my music career. With time, patience, & growth, I will continue to develop into a greater artist. fruitless is just the beginning. 

Big thank you @hadiyadoll for featuring vocals & @samiyyy_ for the sound and guitar chords.
